        zprávu z verifikace (viz 6.2.4.13). (&lt;font lang=&quot;JA&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;LiberationSans&quot;>&lt;font lang=&quot;JA&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&#xD;
        face=&quot;LiberationSans&quot;>7.3.4.41&lt;/font>&lt;/font>)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
