    7.6.4.7 až 7.6.4.10. (&lt;font lang=&quot;JA&quot; size=&quot;2&quot; face=&quot;LiberationSans&quot;>&lt;font lang=&quot;JA&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&#xD;
    face=&quot;LiberationSans&quot;>7.6.4.13&lt;/font>&lt;/font>)&#xD;
&lt;/p></refinedDescription>
